04:57.380 --> 05:00.656
That's alright,
I don't remember yours either.

05:00.900 --> 05:02.128
Shall we go?

05:02.260 --> 05:04.410
- Have you decided where to?
- Let's go to Buzio.

05:04.660 --> 05:05.615
I think I'm going to go.

05:05.740 --> 05:07.810
Come along, you'll get
to know the group!

05:11.020 --> 05:12.339
Alors, tu viens?

05:25.140 --> 05:27.859
Leonor says you came to Sines to write
a book and revolutionise the town.

05:27.980 --> 05:30.448
And that you want to be a poet.
Or was it a painter?

05:30.740 --> 05:32.298
I can't remember.

05:32.940 --> 05:34.737
I'm not good at art.
But I'd love to!

05:35.300 --> 05:36.733
You were in Brussels, weren't you?

05:36.980 --> 05:39.778
I've never left...
IfI could choose...

05:40.740 --> 05:43.937
Paris. I think the ﬁrst place
I'd visit would be Paris.

05:44.300 --> 05:47.133
I'm absolutely sure Paris would love
meeting you, Clara.

05:47.380 --> 05:50.816
- Why? What makes you say that?
- There's something Parisian about you.

05:51.780 --> 05:53.498
Me?! No...

05:53.700 --> 05:56.168
Joao Maria says I look like
Anna Karina, Godard's muse.

05:56.420 --> 05:57.409
